front.title: •A Million Voices Crying Out
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Twice per game may take Commence Primary Ignition into hand from Lost Pile or Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If Alderaan 'blown away,' retrieve 3 Force whenever you deploy a unique (•) Star Destroyer. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: Tarkin silenced the voices of Alderaan with the power of the Death Star.

combo: A Million Voices Crying Out + Set your Course For Alderaan (SYCFA) Objective
